headline.main: U.S. Sees Iraqi Offensive to Retake Mosul in April-May Time Frame
headline.print_headline: U.S. Sees Iraqi Offensive to Retake Mosul in April-May Time Frame

docs.snippet: An Iraqi and Kurdish military force of some 20,000 to 25,000 troops is being prepared to recapture the city of Mosul from Islamic State fighters, probably in the April-May time frame, an official at the U.S. Central Command said on Thursday....
docs.lead_paragraph: An Iraqi and Kurdish military force of some 20,000 to 25,000 troops is being prepared to recapture the city of Mosul from Islamic State fighters, probably in the April-May time frame, an official at the U.S. Central Command said on Thursday.
